<br>
Kinda like above.  You are presenting things about me which are not fact and which you either have no means to prove them, or outright you know them to not be fact.  Not only have you slandered me, but you have gone beyond that and implicated every single member of my guild in the same paragraph.  If I receive harassment, or my guild receives harassment due to this, you are at fault, as the things you have said are not true.  Had I, or my guild actually done those things, and you merely brought them to light, I / we would be at fault.  The person in the &quot;wrong&quot; here, is you.  Feel free to look up &quot;slander&quot; in the dictionary.<br>
<br>
&quot;You might not have actually commited the crime, you helped it happen. The places that you get your information from arent posting, they will produce results for a search for those who go looking, but there is a huge difference for those who actually put the information in a public area in order to get retribution. You are basically putting a virtual contract out on the people whose personal info you post.&quot;<br>
<br>
Then we must jail every gun seller.  We must bring some responsibility to knife manufacturers.  Automobile dealers will need to be fined and or jailed.<br>
<br>
&quot;I will give you one final example, a guy goes to war, leaves his wife and children, a person with a grudge decides to look up his wedding certificate, then does a search for matching names, and then cities, and this same person then posts that information say on a site that frequented by the Taliban, to which the Taliban orders a sleeper agent in the US to kill or kidnap the family, you are telling me, if you were the person who did the search and posted the info you wouldnt feel any guilt whatsoever for the reprecussions of your foolish actions?<br>
If you believe that this personal information you feel so ready to post cannot be used to terrible ends, then you are more foolish then I ever thought. You also had a hand in that act happening by helping it happen.&quot;<br>
<br>
Yes lets blow this way out of proportion  : )   Make ya a deal.  If the Taliban goes and kills Jason Leydon, I'll feel bad.  You dumbass.  : P<br>
