&quot;Yes you can argue its a stretch, but so was the idea that terrorists might take planes and plow them through buildings, but when it happened it became a grim reality.<br>
&quot;<br>
<br>
Wasn't a stretch.  I wondered why it hadn't happened sooner.  <br>
<br>
